description:
Specifications

    This is original Nagoya antenna NA-701 144/430Mhz Dual Band High Gain Antenna. Soft
    100% new, factory packed and never been used.
    It is extendable that boost the signal of your radio significantly.
    Specifications:
    Frequency: 144/430MHz
    Gain: 144Mhz  2.15dBi  430Mhz 3.0dBi  
    Max power: 10Watts
    V.S.W.R: Less 1.5
    Impedance: 50 OHM
    Connector: SMA-F
    Length: Normal 211mm
    Weight: 40g
